p%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Washington%20has%20toyed%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund.%20Last%20March%2C%20a%20group%20of%20bipartisan%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elawmakers%20led%20by%20Sen.%20Angus%20King%20and%20Sen.%20Bill%20Cassidy%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsovereign-wealth-fund-biden-sanders-romney-warren-social-security-medicare-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ediscussing%20a%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epay%20for%20Social%20Security.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Sen.%20Mitt%20Romney%2C%20who%20attended%20the%20talks%2C%20said%20the%20fund%20would%20allow%20the%20United%20States%20%26quot%3Bto%20be%20able%20to%20borrow%20at%20low%20interest%20rates%20and%20invest%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20our%20economy%2C%20and%20perhaps%20economies%20of%20other%20nations%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20potential%20uses%20for%20the%20fund%2C%20if%20%E2%80%94%20again%20%E2%80%94%20it%20can%20ever%20be%20funded%2C%20is%20nearly%20unlimited%2C%20which%20excites%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House's%20interest%20in%20a%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20stems%20partly%20from%20its%20desire%20to%20compete%20with%20China%2C%20which%20has%20multiple%20state-owned%20funds%20itself.%20White%20House%20aides%20suggested%20an%20American%20fund%20could%20bolster%20national%20interests%20through%20things%20like%20%26quot%3Bbridge%20financing%26quot%3B%20for%20companies%20competing%20with%20China%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20suggested%20the%20fund%20could%20support%20technologies%20with%20high%20entry%20barriers%2C%20like%20geothermal%20and%20nuclear%20fusion%20projects%20or%20quantum%20cryptography.%20Or%20it%20could%20create%20synthetic%20reserves%20of%20critical%20minerals%20by%20purchasing%20futures%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20hey%2C%20maybe%20it%20could%20even%20be%20used%20to%20pay%20down%20the%20national%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20great%20to%20see%20America%20join%20this%20party%20and%20instead%20of%20having%20debt%2C%20have%20savings%2C%26quot%3B%20billionaire%20John%20Paulson%20said%20last%20week%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20Television.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%2C%20over%20time%2C%20larger%20than%20any%20of%20the%20existing%20funds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20nice%2C%20but%20it%20all%20hinges%20on%20government%20cash%20to%20fund%20it%20and%20sound%20investments%20to%20grow%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Treasury%20Secretary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-reserves-rate-cuts-itchy-fingers-rush-inflation-larry-summers-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELarry%20Summers%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20Television%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elast%20week%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20believe%20that%20setting%20aside%20lots%20of%20funds%20for%20unspecified%20investments%20made%20in%20unspecified%20ways%2C%20where%20you%20don't%20even%20know%20what%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20called%2C%20is%20a%20particularly%20responsible%2C%20kind%20of%20proposal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-and-biden-us-should-have-a-sovereign-wealth-fund-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725827776000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ddbe6aa0ff598b2665a466%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-and-biden-us-should-have-a-sovereign-wealth-fund-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Momentum%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20is%20picking%20up%20to%20establish%20an%20American%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20that%20optimists%20say%20could%20pay%20for%20just%20about%20anything.%22%2C%