20ensure%20justice.%20I%20hope%20that%20people%20will%20be%20with%20us%20since%20they%20are%20the%20main%20source%20of%20our%20strength%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20woman%20were%20part%20of%20the%20march%20held%20by%20the%20medical%20fraternity%20from%20Sealdah%20to%20Esplanade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%204%2C%20the%20woman's%20father%20had%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20deliberately%20delaying%20the%20registration%20of%20a%20First%20Information%20Report.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20a%20police%20officer%20had%20offered%20him%20money%20and%20tried%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20settle%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20another%20officer%20of%20Kolkata%20Police%20of%20deliberately%20trying%20to%20mislead%20people%20through%20incorrect%20media%20statements%20--%20even%20when%20the%20case%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20or%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20they%20had%20also%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20wanted%20to%20preserve%20their%20daughter's%20body%20for%20a%20second%20postmortem%2C%20but%20were%20forced%20to%20cremate%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbout%20300-400%20cops%20surrounded%20us.%20We%20returned%20home%20and%20found%20some%20300%20cops%20were%20standing%20outside.%20They%20created%20such%20a%20situation%20that%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20cremate%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20father%20said%2C%20setting%20off%20a%20major%20political%20row.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20said%20the%20political%20parties%20should%20leave%20the%20bereaved%20parents%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20should%20have%20been%20no%20politics%20here.%20Political%20parties%20should%20not%20bother%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20state%20minister%20Shashi%20Panja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETomorrow%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20hear%20the%20case%20it%20has%20taken%20up%20on%20its%20own%2C%20during%20which%20the%20CBI%20is%20expected%20to%20present%20its%20report.%20The%20case%20was%20also%20heard%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20which%2C%20following%20the%20appeal%20by%20the%C2%A0%20parents%2C%20had%20handed%20the%20investigation%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20protests%20over%20the%20rape-murder%20have%20acquired%20a%20life%20of%20their%20own%2C%20the%20woman's%20parents%20are%20closely%20associated%20with%20it%2C%20and%20appear%20on%20crucial%20days.%20The%20woman's%20mother%2C%20who%20lost%20her%20only%20daughter%2C%20today%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20all%20these%20protesters%20are%20all%20my%20children%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725816480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F7qal58as_kolkata-protest-school-alumni_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolice-tried-to-destroy-evidence-from-start-kolkata-doctors-parents-6520473%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parents%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20doctor%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20killed%20last%20month%2C%20have%20accused%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20of%20attempting%20to%20destroy%20evidence%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolice-tried-to-destroy-evidence-from-start-kolkata-doctors-parents-6520473%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kendrick%20Lamar%20to%20headline%20Super%20Bowl%20half-time%20show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725816441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1a1a%2Flive%2F8ef9b290-6e07-11ef-a2dc-895f7a5aec6d.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2eqlqnyzno%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Grammy-award%20winning%20musician%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20remind%20the%20world%20why%20rap%20music%20is%20the%20%26quot%