Too%20Charge%2C%20Bengal%20Director%20Says%20%26quot%3BWas%20Unintentional%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengali%20filmmaker%20Arindam%20Sil%2C%20who%20was%20suspended%20by%20the%20Directors'%20Association%20of%20Eastern%20India%20(DAEI)%20following%20a%20complaint%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20an%20actor%2C%20has%20denied%20the%20charges%20and%20said%20what%20was%20being%20construed%20as%20misbehaviour%20was%20unintentional.%20He%20said%20he%20never%20took%20it%20that%20way%2C%20and%20the%20alleged%20incident%20happened%20during%20the%20normal%20course%20of%20shooting%20in%20front%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sil%20is%20the%20first%20big%20name%20in%20the%20Bengali%20film%20industry%2C%20also%20called%20Tollywood%2C%20against%20whom%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20DAEI%2C%20following%20a%20massive%20%23MeToo%20movement%20in%20the%20Kerala%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20react%3F%20I%20don't%20know.%20But%20only%20one%20thing%20I%20can%20say%20I%20have%20been%20100%20per%20cent%20clear%20to%20my%20conscience%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20to%20which%20I%20have%20been%20blamed%20is%20something%20that%20has%20happened%20in%20front%20of%20all%20who%20were%20there%20while%20I%20was%20discussing%20a%20sequence%20and%20acting%2C%20how%20a%20scene%20should%20be%20done.%20I%20think%20most%20directors%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sil%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20other%20people%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20though%20shooting%20was%20being%20done%20inside%20a%20room.%20There%20were%20technicians%20too.%20I%20can%20only%20say%20that%20it%20was%20100%20per%20cent%20unintentional.%20But%20the%20other%20party%2C%20she%20might%20have%20felt%20something%20else%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20felt%20it%2C%20absolutely%20not%20felt%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20absolutely%20an%20extremely%20professional%20person%2C%20working%20in%20this%20industry%20for%20years.%20On%20the%20floor%2C%20cinema%20is%20my%20passion%20and%20if%20there%20is%20anything%20that%20has%20to%20be%20shown%2C%20it's%20done%20very%20clinically.%20That's%20how%20I%20do%20it...%20As%20far%20as%20the%20woman%20is%20concerned%2C%20unintentionally%20if%20I%20have%20hurt%20the%20actor%2C%20then%20I%20am%20sorry.%20Whatever%20I%20spoke%20or%20we%20all%20discussed%2C%20nothing%20was%20videographed%20or%20recorded%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20apology%20letter%20which%20Mr%20Sil%20had%20submitted%20to%20the%20women's%20commission%20that's%20looking%20into%20the%20allegation%20was%20cited%20as%20prima%20facie%20evidence%20by%20the%20DAEI%20in%20suspending%20him%20from%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20he%20plans%20to%20do%20next%2C%20Mr%20Sil%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know.%20Let's%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20had%20filed%20the%20complaint%20with%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Commission%20for%20Women.%20Mr%20Sil%20said%20the%20DAEI%20suspended%20him%20before%20he%20could%20present%20his%20views%20to%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20told%20NEWS18%20Bangla%20that%20she%20had%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20commission.%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20ask%20him%20why%20one%20has%20to%20be%20physical%20to%20explain%20a%20shot%3F%20We%20are%20all%20professional%20actors.%20The%20rest%20I%20will%20state%20before%20the%20commission%20whenever%20needed%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sil%20is%20known%20for%20his%20detective%20films%20such%20as%20'Har%20Har%20Byomkesh'%20and%20'Mitin%20Mashi'%2C%20besides%20the%20Shabor%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725815040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Flqj07e5_arindam-sil_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-director-arindam-sil-says-was-unintentional-after-actors-metoo-charge-6519783%22%2C