But%20today%20I%20think%20you%20see%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20that%20boys%20are%20coming%20from%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid%20said%20it's%20getting%20reflected%20in%20the%20standards%20of%20domestic%20cricket%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20just%20look%20at%20the%20standard%20of%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%20In%20the%20old%20days%20when%20you%20played%20in%20the%20South%20Zone%2C%20other%20than%20playing%20Hyderabad%20or%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20I%20think%20it%20is%20fair%20to%20say%2C%20without%20being%20disrespectful%2C%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20teams%20you%20could%20take%20it%20not%20for%20granted%20but%20you%20could%20certainly%20take%20it%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20lightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20any%20team%20in%20the%20South%20Zone%20today%20that%20you%20can%20walk%20in%20and%20say%20that%20you%20will%20comfortably%20beat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20the%20club%20cricket%20structure%20in%20the%20country%2C%20particularly%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Dravid%20said%20the%20system%20has%20allowed%20the%20sport%20to%20remain%20accessible%20to%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20clubs%20to%20be%20strong.%20We%20need%20cricket%20not%20to%20be%20concentrated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few%20people.%20We%20need%20cricket%20to%20be%20egalitarian%2C%20we%20need%20it%20to%20be%20all%20over%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20have%20talent%20or%20you%20cannot%20have%20facilities%20concentrated%20only%20in%20one%20or%20two%20places.%20To%20get%20the%20best%20out%20of%20talent%2C%20we%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20young%20boys%20and%20girls%20are%20getting%20access%20to%20good%20infrastructure%20in%20every%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2051-year-old%20former%20Indian%20captain%20then%20briefly%20revisited%20his%20club%20career%20when%20he%20was%20young%20to%20underscore%20the%20need%20for%20that%20system%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20practice%2C%20HAL%20(Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited)%20would%20give%20us%20two%20eggs%20and%20one%20small%20glass%20of%20milk.%20I%20would%20always%20stay%20back%20for%20that%20glass%20of%20milk%20and%20those%20eggs.%20Not%20because%20I%20wanted%20the%20milk%20and%20eggs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20sit%20and%20listen%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20BK%20Kumar%20or%20Nandan%20talking%20about%20cricket.%20And%20it%20used%20to%20be%20great%20fun%20to%20listen%20to%20them%20and%20learn%20so%20much%20from%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dravid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725808740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F6nl34d6_rahul-dravid-bcci_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwithout-being-disrespectful-rahul-dravids-big-take-on-domestic-cricket-6517862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20legendary%20Rahul%20Dravid%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20Indian%20cricket%20has%20evolved%20into%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20powerful%26quot%3B%20force%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20growing%20talent%20pool.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwithout-being-disrespectful-rahul-dravids-big-take-on-domestic-cricket-6517862%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sudan%20rejects%20UN%20call%20for%20peace%20force%20to%20protect%20civilians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725808436000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3a62%2Flive%2Fbe1fcc90-6de8-11ef-9033-3948a5d523ee.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc93