tion%20%E2%80%94%20people%20deserve%20to%20be%20happy.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20things%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20would%20never%20be%20the%20same%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20break%20up%20was%20also%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280872caa-f2c6-45fc-8fef-feeb8eec9abe%5C%22%3EA%20clean%20split%20was%20impossible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20the%20lines%20in%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20tend%20to%20be%20clearer%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20cleaner%2C%20less%20painful%20split%2C%20where%20the%20friends%20you%20bring%20into%20a%20relationship%20are%20the%20ones%20you%20leave%20with.%20In%20this%20situation%2C%20we%20were%20so%20deeply%20enmeshed%20in%20each%20other's%20lives%20that%20a%20clean%20split%20was%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20emotional%20labor%20has%20been%20put%20on%20the%20parties%20not%20involved%20to%20navigate%20social%20events.%20We%20try%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20tears%20are%20shed%20on%20birthdays%2C%20and%20to%20make%20sure%20everyone%20feels%20included%20and%20supported.%20This%20gets%20thornier%20as%20our%20friends%20venture%20into%20dating%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20accommodate%20the%20feelings%20of%20other%20new%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20year%20since%20the%20separation%2C%20the%20dust%20has%20begun%20to%20settle%2C%20and%20the%20relationship%20dynamics%20are%20calcifying%2C%20thanks%2C%20in%20large%20part%2C%20to%20self-selection.%20As%20with%20any%20breakup%2C%20things%20get%20easier%20with%20time%3B%20I%20never%20expected%20to%20experience%20those%20same%20feelings%20about%20someone%20else's%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20we%20were%20all%20together%20before%20the%20separation%20was%20a%20weekday%20in%20September%20%E2%80%94%20mere%20weeks%20before%20the%20break%20up%20%E2%80%94%20enjoying%20the%20last%20few%20days%20warm%20enough%20to%20sit%20around%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20pool%2C%20dangling%20our%20feet%20into%20the%20cool%20water.%20We%20drank%20wi