%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fhealth%2Fhealth-ministry-reports-first-suspected-case-of-mpox-virus-in-india-124090800399_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP's%20Gag%20Order%20On%20Brij%20Bhushan%20As%20Wrestlers%20Join%20Congress%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20asked%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20to%20take%20care%20not%20to%20create%20any%20row%20with%20comments%20at%20wrestlers%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20BJP%20MP%20faced%20allegations%20of%20sex%20harassment%20from%20some%20of%20the%20top%20athletes%20in%20the%20country%20including%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20has%20alleged%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20were%20a%20conspiracy%20hatched%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20pointing%20at%20Ms%20Phogat%20and%20wrestler%20Bajrang%20Punia%20joining%20the%20Congress%20party%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Mr%20Punia%20and%20Ms%20Phogat)%20were%20the%20faces...%20they%20were%20mohrey%20(pawns).%20They%20were%20used%20like%20pawns%20by%20(former%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister)%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Congress%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20all%20conspired%20to%20gain%20a%20hold%20on%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20and%20to%20attack%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideology...%20This%20team%20of%20Rahul%20(Gandhi)%2C%20the%20Congress%20keeps%20doing%20these%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202012%20when%20Mr%20Singh%20first%20got%20control%20of%20the%20WFI%20after%20a%20bitter%20turf%20war%20with%20Mr%20Hooda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Mr%20Singh's%20latest%20comments%2C%20the%20BJP%20asked%20him%20not%20to%20pass%20any%20more%20comments%20against%20the%20wrestlers%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20sends%20a%20large%20number%20of%20sportspersons%20to%20national%20teams.%20Athletes%20in%20the%20state%20are%20seen%20to%20command%20large%20loyal%20followers%2C%20and%20this%20may%20have%20prompted%20the%20BJP%20to%20caution%20its%20former%20MP%20to%20keep%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20does%20not%20want%20to%20see%20any%20new%20narrative%20linked%20to%20the%20wrestlers'%20protest%2C%20which%20had%20drawn%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20in%20Haryana%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20give%20Mr%20Singh%20a%20ticket%20from%20Kaiserganj%20and%20made%20his%20son%20Karan%20Bhushan%20Singh%20the%20candidate%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Bhushan%20Singh%20won%20the%20election%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%201.48%20lakh%20votes%2C%20defeating%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Bhagat%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20both%20Ms%20Phogat%20and%20Mr%20Punia%20said%20they%20would%20continue%20the%20fight%20against%20Mr%20Singh%20with%20the%20former%20asserting%20she%20would%20ensure%20that%20no%20woman%20faces%20what%20she%20had%20to%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year-old%2C%20who%20is%20a%20two-time%20world%20championships%20medallist%20besides%20being%20an%20Asiad%20gold-winner%2C%20will%20contest%20from%20Julana%20constituency.%20Mr%20Punia%20has%20been%20made%20the%20working%20chairman%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725796020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffl8er4oo_brij-bhushan-sharan-singh_625x300_13_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-gag-order-on-brij-bhushan-as-wrestlers-join-congress-ahead-of-haryana-polls-sources-6518618%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20asked%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhu