0approach%20proved%20effective%2C%20as%20many%20students%20who%20discovered%20his%20free%20lessons%20on%20Pornhub%20went%20on%20to%20enrol%20in%20his%20paid%20courses%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hsu%2C%20who%20operates%20under%20the%20handle%20changshumath666%2C%20has%20a%20verified%20account%20on%20Pornhub.%20Under%20his%20channel%20slogan%20%26quot%3BPlay%20Hard%2C%20Study%20Hard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20creatively%20repurposes%20the%20adult%20website%20to%20make%20complex%20calculus%20concepts%20accessible%20to%20a%20wider%20audience.%C2%A0Interestingly%2C%20his%20Pornhub%20channel%20has%20now%20become%20a%20go-to%20destination%20for%20many%20students%20seeking%20to%20grasp%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20calculus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20unconventional%20approach%2C%20the%20teacher%20previously%20told%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmelmagazine.com%2Fen-us%2Fstory%2Fmath-lessons-on-pornhub%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMel%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20''Since%20very%20few%20people%20teach%20math%20on%20adult%20video%20platforms%2C%20and%20since%20there%20are%20so%20many%20people%20who%20watch%20videos%20on%20them%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20if%20I%20uploaded%20my%20videos%20there%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20would%20see%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20video%2C%20the%20teacher%20appears%20in%20his%20signature%20grey%20hoodie%20and%20glasses%2C%20exuding%20quiet%20confidence%20as%20he%20tackles%20complex%20mathematical%20problems%20on%20a%20green%20board.%C2%A0His%20videos%20tend%20to%20last%20around%2040%20minutes%20and%20net%20around%2020%2C000%20viewers%20per%20clip%20on%20average.%C2%A0%20However%2C%20the%20teacher%20estimates%20that%20over%2060%25%20of%20his%20audience%20tunes%20in%20for%20entertainment%20value%20rather%20than%20a%20genuine%20interest%20in%20learning%20complex%20mathematical%20concepts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''People%20may%20not%20be%20interested%20in%20my%20videos%2C%20but%20they'll%20all%20know%20there's%20a%20teacher%20who%20teaches%20calculus%20on%20an%20adult%20video%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20admitted%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20further%20broaden%20his%20reach%20by%20uploading%20his%20math%20lessons%20to%20other%20adult%20websites.%20However%2C%20his%20efforts%20were%20met%20with%20resistance.%20According%20to%20Hsu%2C%20these%20platforms%20have%20sophisticated%20content%20moderation%20systems%20in%20place%2C%20which%20enabled%20them%20to%20swiftly%20identify%20and%20remove%20his%20non-adult%2C%20educational%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20initial%20hurdles%2C%20his%20decision%20to%20market%20his%20math%20lessons%20on%20Pornhub%20yielded%20significant%20financial%20rewards.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffocustaiwan.tw%2Fsociety%2F202111020009%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3EFocus%20Taiwan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20revealed%20that%20his%20online%20teaching%20endeavours%2C%20which%20now%20span%20multiple%20platforms%2C%20generate%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20approximately%20%24270%2C000.%20He%20utilises%20the%20earnings%20to%20cover%20his%20living%20expenses%2C%20pay%20his%20bills%2C%20and%20provide%20a%20stable%20salary%20to%20his%20employees%2C%20who%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20helping%20him%20develop%20and%20deliver%20educational%20content%20across%20his%20various%20platforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20didn't%20want%20to%20teach%20math%20on%20Pornhub.%20I%20wanted%20to%20let%20the%20world%20know%20that%20I'm%20a%20teacher%20from%20Taiwan%20who%20can%20teach%20calculus%20well%2C''%20he%20further%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725795780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ffa6054a_taiwan-math-teacher_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftaiwan-teacher-earns-rs-2-crore-a-year-b