0class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECatering%20to%20150%20cities%20worldwide%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20company%2C%20Bishwadeep%20shares%20that%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299084%2Fdesigner-upcycles-scrap-fabric-into-trendy-clothes-bags-lets-save-as-anshika-yadav%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20fabric%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20sourced%20from%20garment%20factories%2C%20it%20is%20sorted%2C%20cut%2C%20and%20transformed%20by%20these%20refugee%20artisans%20into%20dolls%20and%20other%20home%20decor%20items%3B%20incorporating%20traditional%20embroidery%2C%20sewing%2C%20and%20crocheting%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handcrafted%20dolls%20reflect%20the%20personalities%20and%20stories%20of%20the%20artisans%2C%20making%20each%20creation%20a%20symbol%20of%20resilience%20and%20creativity.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20all%20handwork%20and%20each%20doll%20reflects%20the%20unique%20personalities%20of%20the%20artisan%20who%20crafted%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESilaiWali%20participates%20in%20trade%20shows%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Paris%2C%20boosting%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20global%20market.%20With%20this%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20able%20to%20tap%20into%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20these%20dolls%20in%20150%20cities%20worldwide%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Japan%2C%20Korea%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20and%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Goa%20within%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCfA9pX3DaB2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCfA9pX3DaB2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cd